OL,5, A dad died after saving his young son  
OL,6, from drowning in the sea, his grieving 
OL,7, partner has revealed.                  
OL,9,FDavid Cole and his three-year-old boy  
OL,10,Fwere caught by a rip tide while at a   
OL,11,Fbeach in West Mersea on 11 June.       
OL,13,FThe 30-year-old made sure his son was  
OL,14,Funharmed, keeping his head above water,
OL,15,Fbut Mr Cole never regained             
OL,16,Fconsciousness.                         
OL,18,FHis partner, Katie Macdonald, is       
OL,19,Fraising money for the Royal National   
OL,20,FLifeboat Institution (RNLI).           
